summary: The video showcases aviation terminology, featuring pilots in a cockpit and on the tarmac. It defines terms like PAX (Passengers), ILS (Instrument Landing System), MDA (Minimum Descent Altitude), ETD (Estimated Time of Departure), and GS (Ground Speed).
transcript: Do you speak aviation? Let's find out. Pax. Passengers. ILS. Instrument landing system. MDA. Minimum descent altitude. ETD. Estimated time of departure. GS. Ground speed.
